# Visual design — tekkisma.es

Dark editorial portfolio. **Single source of truth:** `src/style.css` (`:root` tokens) + `tailwind.config.js` (maps tokens to utilities).

## Token map

| Layer | Where | Use |
|-------|--------|-----|
| Colors | `--c-brand-*`, `--c-surface*`, `--c-ink*` | Tailwind: `brand-*`, `surface`, `ink`, `accent`, `line` |
| Dividers | `--alpha-divider`, `--alpha-divider-strong` | `border-line`, `.divider-faint` |
| Fonts | `--font-sans`, `--font-mono`, `--font-gallifreyan` | `font-sans`, `font-mono`, `font-gallifreyan` |
| Radii | `--radius-sm` … `--radius-xl` | `rounded-sm` … `rounded-xl` |
| Shadows | `--shadow-card`, `--shadow-media`, `--shadow-cover`, `--glow-accent` | `shadow-card`, `shadow-media`, `shadow-cover`, `shadow-glow` |
| Motion | `--ease-out`, `duration-280`, `ease-out` | transitions |

**Never** hardcode `rgb(249 115 22)` — use `rgb(var(--c-brand-500) / …)` or `brand-500` / `accent`.

## Semantic classes (prefer over raw `text-3xl`)

| Class | Role |
|-------|------|
| `.page-section` | Standard view shell (`max-w-content`, padding top) |
| `.title-section` | Page `h1` in `SectionHeading` |
| `.title-row` | Blog list titles |
| `.title-article` | Article hero title |
| `.title-empty` | Empty / 404 states |
| `.text-emphasis` | Large inline emphasis (e.g. email) |
| `.text-body` | Body copy |
| `.text-meta` | Mono date / metadata |
| `.display`, `.headline`, `.kicker` | Home hero scale |
| `.accent-rule`, `.accent-rule--sm/md` | Orange horizontal bars |
| `.empty-state` | Dashed empty panels only |
| `.link-back` | Text back navigation + arrow |
| `.divider-faint` | List row separators |

Gallifreyan overrides target these classes — add new headings to `html.locale-gallifreyan` block in `style.css`.

## Avoid “box with border”

Default **no** to framed cards for layout. Use typography, grids, `.accent-rule`, gradient washes, left rails.

`Card.vue` / `.empty-state` are intentional bordered surfaces — not the default layout tool.

## Personality & motion

- Deterministic marks from content (`blogPostMark`, slug hash)
- `user-select: none` on decorative glyphs
- `RevealBlock`, `duration-280`, `ease-out`; respect `prefers-reduced-motion`
- ES/EN locale codes stay **Latin** (`font-mono`) in Gallifreyan mode

## Quick check

1. Generic SaaS card? → rework.
2. New color/radius/shadow? → add token first, then Tailwind extend if needed.
3. Matches an existing semantic class?
